<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-darkblue mb-2">欢迎来到AppName！</h1>
<p class="text-lg text-secondary mb-8">您的全能应用，助力高效与乐趣。</p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-8 items-stretch justify-center mb-10">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 min-w-[180px] text-center flex-1 max-w-xs flex flex-col items-center">
    <div class="font-semibold text-darkblue mb-2">App Store</div>
    <img src="<%= generate_qr(@app_store_url) %>" alt="App Store QR" class="bg-white p-2 rounded-lg border-2 border-primary w-28 h-28 mx-auto mb-2">
    <a href="<%= @app_store_url %>" class="button mt-2" target="_blank">前往 App Store</a>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 min-w-[180px] text-center flex-1 max-w-xs flex flex-col items-center">
    <div class="font-semibold text-darkblue mb-2">Google Play</div>
    <img src="<%= generate_qr(@play_store_url) %>" alt="Google Play QR" class="bg-white p-2 rounded-lg border-2 border-primary w-28 h-28 mx-auto mb-2">
    <a href="<%= @play_store_url %>" class="button mt-2" target="_blank">前往 Google Play</a>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 min-w-[180px] text-center flex-1 max-w-xs flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
    <div class="font-semibold text-darkblue mb-2">APK 直装包</div>
    <a href="<%= @apk_url %>" class="button mt-2" download>下载 APK</a>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="bg-yellow-100 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 rounded-lg p-5 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
  <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-darkblue mb-2">温馨提示</div>
  <div class="text-darkblue text-base leading-relaxed">
    如果您在中国大陆地区，<span class="font-bold text-secondary">请将您的 App Store 区域切换到中国大陆以外</span>，即可通过 App Store 或 Google Play 下载本应用。<br>
    如果您使用安卓手机且不想切换区域，可以直接下载 <span class="font-bold text-secondary">APK 直装包</span> 进行安装。
  </div>
</div>
<h2 class="text-2xl text-secondary font-bold mb-6">应用特色</h2>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 justify-center">
  <% @feature_images.each_with_index do |img, i| %>
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 text-center w-48">
      <img src="<%= img %>" alt="功能<%= i+1 %>" class="w-40 rounded-md border-2 border-primary bg-white mb-3 mx-auto">
      <div class="text-base text-darkblue font-medium">功能<%= i+1 %></div>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div> 